      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "Which isomer would you expect to undergo E2 elimination faster, <i>trans</i>-1-bromo-4-<i>tert</i>-butylcyclohexane or <i>cis</i>-1-bromo-4-<i>tert</i>-butylcyclohexane? Draw each molecule in its more stable chair conformation, and explain your answer.",
